headline.print_headline: Isner Advances to 4th Round at French Open
headline.main: Isner Advances to 4th Round at French Open

lead_paragraph: John Isner became the first American man to reach the French Open's fourth round since 2010, beating 17th-seeded Tommy Robredo of Spain 7-6 (13), 7-6 (3), 6-7 (5), 7-5 Friday.
